sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Class Timetable Management Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open class timetable management page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Load institute/campus/programme/module/class options
    DB-->>LW: Option lists
    LW-->>UI: Render filters and timetable editor

    User->>UI: Change filters (institute/campus/programme/class/module)
    UI->>LW: updated* handlers
    LW->>DB: Re-query valid options and current events
    DB-->>LW: Filtered options + events
    LW-->>UI: Re-render event rows

    User->>UI: Save timetable changes
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Upsert submitted events + delete removed events
    DB-->>LW: Persist completed
    LW-->>UI: Success toast
